{"id":136077,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/02/路透社明天即将公布的1月份cpi据传在4-9，新算法降低/","date":"2011-02-14T18:21:24Z","modified":"2011-02-14T18:21:24Z","title":"路透社:明天即将公布的1月份CPI据传在4.9%，新算法降低了食品和住房价格的权重","content":"<p><p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/rbRGbjyEkzzAfympYg7HSjcDEuY/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/rbRGbjyEkzzAfympYg7HSjcDEuY/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/rbRGbjyEkzzAfympYg7HSjcDEuY/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/rbRGbjyEkzzAfympYg7HSjcDEuY/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p>China: Rumors floated around in on-shore that CPI’s weighting will change, and thus driving CPI lower to 4.9% (Market previously expecting 5.4% with old methodology) … rumor says food compenent’s weighting’s reduced, and housing is lowered.</p>\n<p>引自路透社，明天即将公布的1月份CPI据传在4.9% ，这是改变了计算方法之后的数据，如果按旧的算法大约在5.3-5.4%之间，新算法降低了食品和住房价格的权重。</p>\n<h2>相关日志</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>2011/01/28 &#8212; <a href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/archives/10583\" title=\"zhuhit:两难\">zhuhit:两难</a> (0)</li>\n<li>2010/12/11 &#8212; <a href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/archives/9561\" title=\"BBC:中国通胀又达新高经济面临过热危机\">BBC:中国通胀又达新高经济面临过热危机</a> (0)</li>\n<li>2010/09/16 &#8212; <a href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/archives/7693\" title=\"阿里巴巴集团研究中心:2010年7月份淘宝CPI指数 – 经济将由热趋冷\">阿里巴巴集团研究中心:2010年7月份淘宝CPI指数 – 经济将由热趋冷</a> (0)</li>\n<li>2010/08/12 &#8212; <a href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/archives/6950\" title=\"许小年:制度性数据失真\">许小年:制度性数据失真</a> (0)</li>\n<li>2009/12/18 &#8212; <a href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/archives/441\" title=\"假如未来cpi > 10%&#8221;>假如未来cpi > 10%</a> (0)</li>\n</ul>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/letscorp/aDmw?a=ZcLCUZxTS1E:Ro2eosQjYao:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/letscorp/aDmw?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/letscorp/aDmw?a=ZcLCUZxTS1E:Ro2eosQjYao:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburne